    <item>
      <title>欧盟准备对电动汽车征收关税，德国警告不要设置贸易壁垒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/germany-warns-against-trade-barriers-as-eu-readies-ev-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧盟即将对从中国进口的电动汽车征收关税之际，德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨表示反对限制汽车贸易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/germany-warns-against-trade-barriers-as-eu-readies-ev-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 13:52:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加沙中部袭击事件后以色列军队释放四名人质</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/israeli-forces-free-four-hostages-after-attack-in-central-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军方于周六在对中部城市努塞拉特发动大规模攻击时，释放了被哈马斯关押在加沙地带的四名人质。哈马斯控制的政府媒体办公室称，至少有 210 名巴勒斯坦人在激烈战斗中丧生，其中包括儿童。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/israeli-forces-free-four-hostages-after-attack-in-central-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 11:20:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>袭击丹麦首相后，男子被判入狱并受到指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/danish-prime-minister-cancels-eu-election-events-after-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名 39 岁的男子因袭击丹麦首相梅特·弗雷德里克森并导致其取消多次选举活动而被监禁，并被指控对官员实施暴力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-08/danish-prime-minister-cancels-eu-election-events-after-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 08:53:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
